properties.Name: ProductRatingFactor
properties.Description:
The rating factor(s) applicable to the Insurance Product.

Each of the applicable rating factors should be applied to the base premium in order to determine the applicable policy premium.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: ProductRatingFactorTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Definition Type.

Columns.Name: ProductRatingFactorNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the Product Rating Factor.
